    A stylized combat idle animation. The
    character has a firm grip on a large, heavy rocket launcher resting on their
    shoulder. They maintain a low, wide, and stable stance with knees slightly bent.
    The animation loop includes confident, rhythmic breathing that moves the chest
    and shoulders, causing the heavy weapon to sway slightly but realistically. The
    character subtly shifts their weight from one foot to the other in an energetic,
    ready-for-action pose.

'
